HEADWORD: igniter
<hw>igniter</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a substance used to
ignite or kindle a fire.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ignitor, lighter.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a device for lighting or igniting fuel or charges or
fires.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lighter, light, ignitor.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ignitible</ent>⟦br⟧
